\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217060/extras/ad031d454a0860a33cb3f388cb30eeba.poster.avif?t=1678395558\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217060/extras/ad031d454a0860a33cb3f388cb30eeba.webm?t=1678395558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>And from the Adventure Game side:</strong><br><br>• Form relationships and choose which companions will accompany you.<br><br>• Learn skills to solve familiar and unfamiliar puzzles and mysteries.<br><br>• And make tough decisions which will twist and turn the narrative.",
